data.description: Well maintained single level home in quiet location on a large lot featuring a private backyard, RV parking, a 10x20 outbuilding, covered deck and hot tub, newer exterior paint and a five year old roof. Inside there is an open floor plan, high ceilings, fully updated kitchen with stainless appliances, granite counter tops, new cupboards and fixtures, three bedrooms and an office space, a large primary suite, updated bathroom fixtures and vaulted ceilings. This home is move in ready and waiting for you! Open House 11/11/23 from 2:30pm to 4:30pm
